Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.96,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I have a big gun
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.69,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I took it from my lord
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.28,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Sick with justice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.17,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I just wanna feel you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.83,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm your angel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.53,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Only a ring away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.31,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}You make me violate you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.77,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}No matter who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.41,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's all up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.95,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}No one lives forever
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.69,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Been burnt in the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.46,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}By all those pigs out there
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.11,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}It's always been hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.77,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}From when I was born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.31,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}They make me violate them
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.98,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}No matter who they are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.41,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get down on your knees
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.18,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Get a good head on your shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.82,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}If it's for your guys
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.61,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Go to the end of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.16,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Do what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.92,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Give it with dedication
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.80,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'll put out your misery
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.43,OP_E,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}Weapon... I have it all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:21.96,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我有一把威力無比的槍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.96,0:00:23.69,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這是上天賜予我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.69,0:00:25.28,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所謂正義讓我感到作嘔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:27.17,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我只想感受你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.83,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我是你的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.53,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是失去了光環
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.53,0:00:32.31,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}褻瀆你 是你自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.31,0:00:33.77,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不管你是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.41,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}這裡由你做主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:43.95,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無人可以永生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:45.69,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在地獄裡承受灼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:47.46,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就因為那些圍觀的鼠輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:49.11,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}自我出生以來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.77,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直生活在地獄中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.77,0:00:52.31,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}褻瀆他們 是他們自找的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.98,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不管他們是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:02.41,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}給我跪下來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:04.18,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}給我放聰明些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:05.82,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如果你們還想要小命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.61,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就給我滾到天邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.16,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}放手做你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:10.92,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}儘管去全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:14.80,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我將為你驅逐痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:29.43,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,400)}武器 這就是我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:37.62,mark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}現場作戰行動區域-D446\N越南廣治省 1969
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.64,0:01:39.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道為什麼我只留下這個小妞嗎 少尉長官
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.77,0:01:48.27,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧 現在才來扮演西部荒野的孤膽騎警麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.86,0:01:59.03,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你也只是想上那個小妞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:02.78,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 也好 按照順序來說也應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.78,0:02:06.51,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是個連下三濫都不如的變態而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.56,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你碰到這個女孩的一根手指的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.45,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 拉金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.81,0:02:18.99,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:53.95,mark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,400)}26年之後\N委內瑞拉 巴裡納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.55,zw,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Hotel·Quebec」
